OtherComments.Content: Maths Symbols The script sets the glyphs to a fixed width and centres them. Change the width to the advance width of the figures in your font. Maths and some Currency symbols are often all the same width as figures. Vertical arrows can also fit well on the figure width. Remove any glyphs that you do not want to resize from the script.
